    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.03249.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>1524 Walnut Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Philadelphia</name>
                </dateline>
                <salute><handShift rend="manuscript"/>My Dear Good Gray Poet&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Ever since I bought the first edition of Leaves of Grass we have been friends through
                your books&#8212;I warmly thank you for this precious memorial of a man whose life
                work + example are better even than<pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.03249.002.jpg"
                    type="verso"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.03249.003.jpg" type="recto"/><pb xml:id="leaf002v"
                    facs="loc.03249.004.jpg" type="verso"/> his books</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>and I am</salute>
                <salute>gratefully</salute>
                <salute>yr. friend</salute>
                <signed>Weir Mitchell</signed>
                <name type="place">Walt. Whitman</name>
                <date when="1889-12-15">Dec 15, 1889</date>
            </closer>


            <pb xml:id="leaf003r" facs="loc.03249.005.jpg" type="recto"/>
